The Falkland Islands have their official currency, the Falkland Islands pound (FKP), whose value equals the British pound (GBP).
The only bank, located in Stanley in front of the FIC West store, offers currency exchange service.
British pounds are generally accepted everywhere on the islands. At Stanley you can often pay with credit cards and US dollars.
